text:
Hello Ji...
Pheli baar mulakat hui thi unn thand bhari raato m, jab pet mai chuhe kuda krte the aur DOAA canteen k bhaiya unhe shaant kiya krte the. Tab toh tuje hindi bhi nahi aati thi saath me. Yuhi milna jhula chalta raha tha second year Antaragni tak jab raakhi ka prastav nahi aaya... woh din hai aur aaj ka din hai!!!

Kisse toh sahi m kam nahi hai... college m bada hua wing m, jeena sikhaya dramatics ne, pr life m jo adventures aaye hai, usme hamesha tera haath tha...

1. SSAC: irada bura nahi tha pr washroom m bag bhulna teri hi galti thi... jiska course ka paper tha, usi ke notes the yrr... DOSA ne confession likhyava tha mere se.. pr end m kuch nahi hua.. hehe.. 

2. IITB: Woh mumbai ki thandi thandi hava kisme jal gaye the hum, nahi bhul sakta mai.

3. Amrita + Savitri: Best part of life. Yeh do plays ki jagah mere jeevan m alag hai. Dono m hi meri fan thi tu... Amrita ne bhi mere ko support kiya aur Savitri toh naam se aur kaam se, dono se Savitri thi... Aur aisa hi kuch kirdar mere asal jeevan m bhi raha hai!!!

4. MTH m dual: yeh pata nahi kyu hua, kaise hua, pr ho gaya. Maine socha tha Data Science krunga pr yeh toh dhoka ho gaya mere saath

5. Intern nahi lagi yrr: Yeh samay toh kaise kata hai, yaad krta hu toh lgta hai, apun hi bhagvaan hai!!  

Aur bhut saare kisse hai. Multipurpose k bahar 1st and 7th scene ki practice krna. yaad hai tere ko lucknow airport lene aaye the.. itne saare gifts diye hai (aur mere kaafi pending bhi hai, jaldi hi saare krta hu)... treats toh itni kri hai pucho mat... woh drameve 2 m kutte bane the- govinda govinda govinda  govinda  govinda  govindaaaaaa......

Pr ek baat mai bata du, tere ko data science ka bhut mere se hi laga hai, yeh baat apne baccho ko bhi batana..  (2 saal lead krne ka ghamand nahi le sakta, toh iss baat ka hi le leta hu..)

Abhi ek saal aur hai campus, acche se enjoy kro, research paper chhapo (inti intern, inte projects ka kya kregi jetti), naukri lagavao croreo ki.... phir saath m treat krenge...

Isi tarah yaad krte rehena, milte rehena on every stage of my life!!

OSTWAL

text:
Yo Moond. Apni to itni memories hai kya kya hi likhu. Apne room se zayda to shyad mai tere room pe hi raha hounga first year se hi. First year me apan exam dene se phle my **** sun ke jaate the enthu badhane ke lie. Lol yaad hai 1st year summer me apan gye the e-club ka test dene aur hume nhi lia tha aur R****** ko le lia tha. Humne maximum course saath me hi kie hain aur tu mujhe cycle pe bitha ke le jata tha. 2nd year udghosh me mere meme banane ke baad lo*** ne chutiyapa kia tha fir tune id banai thi. Bahut bakchod thi wo id waise. Bhola tujhe vc na karta to aur use hota us id ka. 
Best time apna to 2nd year summer hi raha hai. Pure din bas bulla session chalte rehte the. Ek baar mai tu jai mil ke tujhe shaadi se bhagane ki planning kar rhe the jiska kharcha teri bmw bech ke aata. 3rd year ka winter bhi apna bahut interesting hi raha tha. Pehle quiz ko leke batti gang me dispute hua. Phir tune chapa dia tha jisko sun ke mai full shocked tha. Phir prank ke chakkar me batti gang me phir dispute hua tha. Jisko sort karne ke lie maine bahut lamba msg likha tha jo tu maan nhi rha tha ki maine likha hai. ( Ab to maan lena, wo maine khud se hi likha tha) In sab ko mast new year party ke saath conclude kia tha. 
Uske baad to lockdown me hi beet gya pichla saal. Abhi mai last me aaya hota to maza aata but koi nhi apan to milte hi rahenge. 
PS: Humesha aise hi logic lagate rehna.

text:

text:
"Bhai itna sexy kaise hai tu" You and me whenever and wherever we saw each other.

I don't know how, it was mostly because you kept pushing me for good, but we became really good friends from that awkward dance in Antaragni of 2018 where I first met you guys â™¥. You have always helped me in campus and off campus as well, especially during the placements season when I used to be scared and you always used to support me. It has been because of friends like you that I have been able to achieve whatever I have. I don't want you to think this of as a thank you, goodbye vala note. text:
"Damn.... Masala mamgie?? It's hot....... Pff.... Ehh............" - Raj Nandini while eating maggie from Chomcy room.
Yup, we have come a long way from being partners in TA202, which tbh non of us remembers, but it is where our story begins. 3rd semester, being an introvert, it was already difficult for me to retain old friends, leave alone making new ones. But this is when we met (rather an insignificant meeting at hall 3 cc). Who would have thought that a meeting like that would be the start of a lifetime of memories, adventures (BPI), discoveries (still you don't remember IITK map :P), a brand new "lenguez", trust, love, and night outs. My journey at IITK has been a rollercoaster ride, had it been not with you it would have been just a downhill because you were always there for me in my lowest and also at my highest peaks. You are genuinely the most loving and caring person I ever came across and I will forever be grateful to you for each and everything you did for me, be it as little as teaching me in the lambrary before exams or accompanying me for a shamke at mamamio. This past month was this beautiful castle that one works to build his entire life, changing the meaning associated with each place. For me bad memories being replaced by joyous moments and places meaning more than just places. The last night walk that we had made me realise how quickly the good time went, how little we had and how much we made out of it. As strange as it may seem, we will always have a shortage of time and opportunities but as I learnt from you we will make sure to make the most out of them even if it means faking smiles and acting strongly in front of you so that you feel everything is fine as I have done till now. Yes, there were many things that I couldn't write here (including most of our time at OMT :P) but we still have many adventures to look forward to and make memories along the way so buckle up for this new phase of life with which we have many expectations. See you soon! â¤

Pehli mulaakaat to bhulne se rahe, 22nd July 2017, humara baap gayab tha, ek pal ko to laga tha Shreesheil hi baap hota to acha hota room tak chodne to aaya tha. Halaki ab lagta hai kitna galat tha mai, par tumhare room 128 me hi chaen ke kuch saans guzaar raha tha ke tum chaukhat pe dikhe saaman lekar. "Rajasthan ka hoga ye..." mai soch raha tha kyunki man me dhaarna yahi thi ke saavla, patla ladka, hindi bolne vala zyadatar Rajasthani hi hota hai. Us waqt to humare bich zyada baate hui nahi thi aur laga tha ke zyada hongi bhi nahi kyunki hum log alag room ke jo the.... Ab lagta hai kitna galat tha mai. Ye galtiyon ka silsila thama thode tha, kuch galtiyan mujhse bhi hui thi, kuch galat fehmiyan bhi thi kabhi kisi mukaam par. 
Lekin canteen ke silsilo ne, chai ki chuskiyon ne, vo aalu paranthe aur dahi ke khane ne mere ya tumhare vaha is intezar me baithna ke "ye bkl aur kitni der lagayega" se "Thode der aur baith jaate hai" bana diya tha.
Choti choti baate hi to humari is kaahaani ko jitna chahu utni baar padne layak banati hai, chahe vo canteen ho ya wing me ho rahi politics ki ninda karna, diwar pe batman banane se lekar Yogi ke IIT aane ke uplaksh me karakriti karna, "aap kuch nahi jante ho" ya raat ke 2 baje tera room pe aakar "uth bkl canteen chal" bolna ho. Ye yaade sanjho ke rakhi hai maine. Mast maula hai tu, duniya ki reet pe chalne ke liye bana nahi hai tu, is saamaajh ke liye kuch bada karne ki chah to hai tujhme lekin shareer uski anumati nahi deta, marks ki moh maaya se to mujhse bhi pehle upar uth chuka hai tu, har jashn ki jaan raha hai tu aur rahega bhi humseha.
Itna waqt bitaane ke baad bhi man karta hai ki kaash aur waqt bitaya hota, aur baate ki hoti, aur masti ki hoti, aur chai pi hoti, aur gaaliyan di hoti, ya ek baar daaru to pi hi hoti. Lekin is baat ka dukh nahi rahega, humari mulaakat hoti rahegi vaada raha. Ek baat humesha yaad rakhna à¤¤à¥ à¤¹à¥€à¤°à¤¾ à¤¹à¥ˆà¤‚, à¤¹à¤®à¥‡à¤¶à¤¾ à¤à¤¸à¥‡ à¤¹à¥€ à¤šà¤®à¤•à¤¤à¥‡ à¤°à¤¹à¤¨à¤¾à¥¤

text:
"Aur bhai kya kar raha hai?" - Utsav Akarshan on entering my room
BRO! â™¥
I regret we didn't know each other in the first year in spite of being from the same hall and living nearby. You might not remember our first interaction, so let me help. Somewhere in mid-September Ravi borrowed badminton rackets from you and one of them was broken when he returned it. No! I didn't break it but I accompanied him when he was coming to return them to you, so in 3 bot near room 127 you were a bit upset and angry too and were asking Ravi to pay for it and I said: "chill hai bhai ye sab hota rehta hai and humne nahi toda racket pehle hi tuta tha." 
From such a haphazardly meet to super attractive brozz ğŸ˜† we have come a long way. Straight off the bat, you are THE BEST person I met on campus, I learnt a lot from you. In a way being with you especially in the 3rd and 4th semester changed me as a person, this might seem a bit exaggerated to you but really it's the truth â™¥. Being so cool, humble and down to earth you taught me how one should be, from always helping people in spite of being troubled on your own you taught me what being a part of community means in true sense. And from your sincerity I learnt what being ready for the challenges that life throws at you means. And a lot more.......
Although not only I learnt how to be I also learnt how not to be from you (iykwim). With such a wide array of teachings although unconsciously you were definitely a major reason I was able to survive IITK with such an ease. And stating the obvious CHE without you would have been impossible! ğŸ˜†ğŸ˜† Especially the last semester.

text:
Yo Yonsh! Finally, I am writing this ğŸ˜†, now you may not remember our first interaction obviously so let me start from there only (and no it was not treasure hunt wala mail and that too was not an interaction because koi reply nahi aaya tha :')).
"So... What's you name?", "Yashika", "What's your name?", "Abhishek", "Where are you from Yashika?", "Mangalore, tum kaha se ho?", "I am from Roorkee, and Mangalore to south India me hai na so how can you speak hindi?" and then you chuckled a bit and an awkward silence followed as far as I remember. Meanwhile the counselling service people were doing there season in L16 (Cognizance I think)

From then to today we have come a long way, from the creepy treasure hunt ka mail to second year where you, nandu and utsav became my family and as family were always ready to help me. Many times we don't realize how much little things mean so much in our lives, as little as eating a meal together or even clicking a photo as well as in the case of our campus wali diwali when we three shared our meal together in your room (Egg curry, paneer ki sabzi and roti from sagar dhaba ordered from swiggy) and yes the pictures and videos of that day are enough to bring me to tears. And yes thanks for saving my ECO201 ka midsem ka exam in summers!  
CHE classes were memorable because of it, from sincerely attending classes in the beginning to bunking classes after giving our attendance. Inspite of all that we were always ISPP ğŸ˜†ğŸ˜† vo bhi kabhi nahi hua. Maybe we'll do that in an MBA class but still we'll always be LMPP (Life me phodenge partners :P). 
More than anything else you are one of the closest people in the campus and I always admired you for the gem you are as a person, a friend and how you manage to do so much. Trust me, nandu and me used to discuss that a lot on how to be like Yonsh. ğŸ˜†
In the end, whatever life has planned for all of us, always remeber us and stay in contact :') Bronze ko bhulna mat. Wish you all the best for your future! And let's go on a trip whenever this pandemic gets over â™¥â™¥
With love 
Bronze Brozz

text:
Well, this is one of the hardest memoirs for me to write. I have infinite memories and limited space to sum it all up. Jab orientation mein pata laga tha ki teri AIR 10 hai, I used to brag about it everywhere like "YE MERA BHAI HAI", and within the 4 years ye mere liye literal hogaya hai. I guess you are the only person who can summarise my college life to anyone because you have been the third eye of me during my college stay.
JItna time hum dono ek saath spend kiya hai college mein, I can bet that no other friends or couple would have done the same. You are the most Simple, Humble, Raw, Helpful and the CHAAPU-est guy I've ever met. If someone would ask me what does chaapu in IITK means? "Anany Sharma" will be the answer for it. Its not been a single time that you have let me down and we share the purest form of friendship. Tere raat ke 2 baje BSBE mein hagne ke sessions ho ya becch beech mein dieting ka bhoot savaar hona, I always tried to make fun out of those moments.College mein jitni bakchodi ki hai sab saath hai, chahe wo raat ke 12 baje sudden movie plans ho ya goa, mussoorie, shimla jaisi trips. We have been always together throughout all the ups and downs during the journey, and I cannot imagine my college life without you. Even if i think of it, there is a huge void which can never be filled by anyone else. College toh khatam ho chuka hai lekin apni dosti kabhi khatam nahi hogi, jaldi hi ek aur trip pe waapas se milenge. 
Jaate Jaate ek sher farmana chaahunga-

text:
Writing this memoir won't do justice to the memories and the time I've spent with you back at campus.
You are the most genuine, hardworking, rational and intellectual guy I've met in IIT Kanpur. Whether to the meaningless debates at my room or the one we had in the OAT( sutta ya baccha xD), I really cherish all those moments spent together. Kahin bhi daaru ka plan bane toh I made it sure that you have to be included because you completed the vibe. <3 Cheers to some of the epic trips we went together.
Hindu ka debating experience was something which I will never forget, and if you ever feel like getting one of the most relaxing experience in the world, you know the place xD Maine jitne bhi daring experiences try kiye college mein you were the part of them too xD I miss all those late night walks jab hum saare bhai CCD OAT jaate the and used to discuss random shit. Even after having so many involvements, you made it sure to join us for the party ya kabhi bhi jab hum bahar dinner karne jaate the. Wo movie night and rickshaw ka incident was one the most epic thing and that is how the name "Budhau" originated :P (though on the same night accident bhi hua tha and you know the rest ...)
Seeing you getting accepted by Stanford was genuinely a proud moment for me, I was so happy for you. Maine toh anany se bet bhi lagayi hai ki tu pakka firangi se hi shaadi karega :P 
WE OWE BEAUTIFUL MEMORIES TOGETHER <3
Goodluck for future and hum sab firse jaldi milenge for sure.

text:
Yo Bandar! 
To sabse pehle to bahut jyada aalas karne ke bad I decided to write memoirs. And then I was confused ki start kisse karu, so thought to write off from the closest ones! And you are the first one :) 

Apan dono to jab first time mile the tab se hi hm dono ki vibes itni match karti thi. Tm, Snehan, Archies ye sab se bahut jaldi hi apna interaction comfortable level pe aa gya tha. Apna Bihari dost aur wo v same department wala, mujhe yaad hai 1st year me kitni dafa tere room pe hi aake pada rehta tha. Tu apna sunata tha, main apna. 1st year me then ESC labs karne ke baad aake rant karna sath me aur v bahut sari bakchodi karte the apan. 
Kaafi moments me you stood up by my side, thankful for that. Pure wing me meri sabse achi bonding tere sath hi ban gyi thi 1st year me. Isliye next room partner ke liye tujhse acha koi aur nahi hota. 

2nd year me departmental stuff suru ho gye, apan room ke sath sath labs and sare courses v sath me kar rhe the. Sath me kaafi chill out v kara hmne, cricket khel ke pure pasine me room aana, tera "girlfriend chahiye" ka occasional r***i r**a, sath me gym karna (although apan consistent nahi rhe) ğŸ˜‚, fir gym ke bad aloo ticky (lol), diwali pe room decoration, mera nahi nahane pe tera sunana. Breakfast aur dinner ke liye sath mess jana and conversations during that were a separate fun. 

ESC201 kitna rote rote khatm kiye, Suchitra Mathur ko kitna galiyaya tha Tu. Fir treat kha ke v aaya last me.
Apan aur v kafi sari chizen share kiye hote during the journey of 4 years had I been there in civil. But ye civil main jhel nahi paunga ye 3rd sem realise ho gya tha, although I was lucky enough ki meri department change ho gyi. Fir tum logo ke 4-4 labs hote the aur main akele wing me maze karta ğŸ˜‚

3rd year to apan split ho gye in different wings but still tere room pe aake jab tab door pit ke khulwa ke baith jata tha. Apne routine ko leke tm thoda serious the, Jo maine tmse sikha hai. Apan us wing me v kafi maze kare football, cricket, cards ya random bulla. 
Apan dono ka as such jhagda to mere ko yaad nahi aa rha, but agar kaha suni hota v tha to jaldi hi apan normal ho jate the. 

Are ha ek chiz to reh hi gayi, tera upsc ke taraf dedication. Tu day 1 se soch ke aaya tha ki tujhe yehi karna hai. Actually iss bare me main tujhse kaafi influence hua hu from the first year itself. Aur 2nd year aate aate tak to maine v soch liya tha ki bhai yehi karenge apan. Although baad me apan dono ne situation accordingly chizen decide kara. Tu ghar gya tha to sari NCERTs aur Standard books vagerah utha le aaya tha. Aur apan normal stuff pe v kafi discussion pelte the together.

4th year - yeha to bc apan kaafi disconnect ho gye... I think in the whole lockdown, Kuch counted calls rahe honge. Tu placements me aise v nahi baith rha tha to tujhse ekdum hi interaction low ho gya. But still, tere se kabhi bhi baat ho jata hai to mood chill ho jata hai.
Isi tarah hamesha hasta reh, and I've seen ki Tu stress ache se modulate karta hai. 

Are Ispe to ek incident Yaad aa gya. 
Raghvendra ne tmko aur deo ko milne ke liye bulaya tha aur us raat sale tm pura yehi bolte rahe ki pata nahi kyu bulaya hai kya karega, kya hoga. Main tere ko raat bhar samjhata raha.. lekin us din tera alag hi fata hua tha. 
Phir next day aake tera sunana all about confession and then fir chizen sort ho gyi. Raghvendra ne dono ke marks kaat ke chor diya aur tm ghar me btane se darr rhe the karke.


Aur bhi bahut sari countless memories hai bro, ye memoir kafi nahi hoga uske liye. Mujhe IITK me Tu dost nahi Bhai jaisa mil gya. 

All the best for your future aspirations. I'll be waiting to hear from you about cracking the IAS. 

Whenever you read this and want to talk or rant about anything... Just give me a call. I'll be there for you. â¤ï¸ 
Stay in touch, buddy.

text:
Abe tune kab account banaya!? Itne dino se dhoond rha hu tera aur shrey ka account milta hi nahi xD
Office time k beech likh rha hu lol , ek toh bhai likhne ko itna kuch hai ki aisa lagta hai humesha kuch na kuch reh hi jayega
Mile toh 1st year me bhi the but Synchro, junoon inrerviews se jo shuruat hui thi , junoon synchro ki sponsorship me lag lagke itna kaam kiya tha ki hall-1 me logo ko uthane apan hi jate the xD
FIr aaya humara core team tenure jisme sab starting me enthu me thee, but beech me sab give up kar chuke the Antaragni ki possibility par. Even virtual Antaragni ek formality ki tarah lagti thi. Aisa lagta tha humare sath unfair hua hai On ground Antaragni na karwa pane k karan :P. Ussi time team ko tere jaise festis ki zarurat rehti hai jo kabhi give up nahi karte, tera enthu alag hi level par tha online antaragni ko lekar bhi, admin k fuck ups k karan maine marketing ki possibility par hope chhod di thi, but peechhe se tu aur shrey lage huye the sab sort karne me, fir achanak ek din aaya M-1/2 yaad nahi, tera call aaya gusse me, uss waqt mai bhi gussa hoke ego me chhod deta toh kuch alag scene hote... but yahin antaragni ki feel play me aati hai... uski baat hi alah hai... core team k bhi bohot kum logo me actual feel hoti hai... campus k log samjh hi nhi pate hain ki ye 22 log kaise itne united hokar poore campus me macha dete hain...Antaragni ki feel pure hai... interviews itne brutal hote hi isliye hain ki tum self ka poora notion khatm karke sirf cause k liye committed ho jao... usme logo todte hi isliye hain ki tum poora ego 0 karke harr tenure me fir se naye se seekhkar chapo... bas yahi baat campus me kisiko samjh nahi aati hai team k alawa... Uss din wapas kaam shuru hua apna aur rest is history... all iit fest core teams know internally ki konsa fest bakchod ho gya... jal toh gayi hai ab unki... The fire shall rise again logo k liye ek line hai , core team k lifelong mission...rongte khade hona. Antaragni name ka essence bhi tabhi samjh aata hai jab isme pagalo ki tarah kaam karo... love hate sa relationship hota hai bohot zyada...you work tirelessly, drained all yearlong ,aur voh final night in front of barricading saare struggle ko itna zyada justify and more kara deti hai ki uss experience ko hi actual feel aana kehte hain... uss hi moment me Antar+agni ka true meaning kuch hi selected logo ko pata chal pata hai... uss din antaragni se , uski history and legacy se pyar ho jata hai ... bas aise hi logo se bhari padi thi apni core team.. desiny me kuch aur tha voh alag baat hai ... mai interviews me bas isliye interested nahi rehta hu kyoki mujhe pata hai kisi Y18,Y19 ne voh feeling nahi li hai ajtak, uska birth 3rd year antaragni me hi hota hai aur unhone wahi miss ki hai, unki prep ,ppts, dekhkar pain hota hai ki itni rich , full of life changing emotional legacy shayad hi continue ho paye...But han ek belief hai ki the fire shall rise again is forever... londe apne bakchod hain... apan help kar denge toh sab kara bhi lenge...aur sabse main baat apan aisa hone hi nahi denge ki kabhi danger ho antaragni par... Antaragni humari college life ki identity rahi hai, to identify as an antaragni core team is an absolute earned priviledge in campus. The only team of people that can never be mocked about just because the whole campus know the efforts we put in and what we feel fot it!
The fire within !!

Tum dono roomies me se ek ya to humare room pe hota tha ya fir Deepak aur Shubham ke room par, alag hi scene the tumhare.
Aur bhai mujhe 2nd year tak lagta tha tu nerd hai par uske baad  pta laga ki jalwe hai tere to. Teri stories sunke mai to hairaan reh gya tha. Bada rangeen banda hai tu to, itni cool, funy aur daring kisse expect nahi kiye the terese.
Antaragni me bhi kitna ghoomte the tu, mai aur Dhawal, adventure ki talaash me, zyda adventure to mile nahi par fir bhi maze bahot kiye hai humne.
BBQ aur treats ki bhi bahot acchi memories hai.
Jaldi milte hai aur bakchodi karte hai.
All the best bro, you will get great things.
author: Aditya Singh Rathore

text:
First week se hi teri bakchodi to dikh gayi thi. Har senior se pakde jaana aur fir uske baad koi mast song ya joke sunana, banda to tu bada rangeen hai. Waise to hume dusro ke dukh pe hasna nahi chahiye par jab tu ksi ko roast karta tha, wo best entertainment tha. Waise to tu accha singer hai par wo kehte hai na "excess of anything is harmful", to 1st year me humare room me tere concert thode excess me ho gye the. But I gotta admit, uss time bhi tu bina practice ke bhi puri tarah se khul ke gaata tha.
Aate hi 2 mahine me pehla EDM aa gya tha aur tabse hi har EDM me jo akhand randaap machaya hai hum chaaro ne, jo moves kiye hai!!! Humare moves ka ksi aur ke paas tod nahi hota tha. Har EDM me tu, mai, Deepak aur Shubham late hi pauche hai, par bhai wo 8.15 se 10 tak ka dance hi bahot bhari workout ho jaata tha. Uske baad events ground jaake bandiyan taadne se pehle wapas canteen se kuch khake aana padhta tha.
Aur summer camp me sabse consistant player tha tu, consistantly late aata tha:) Aur bhai kya gareebo waala khana tha summer camp me Hall 2 mess ka, watermelon ke alwa kuch khane ka mann hi nahi karta tha, par fir bhi tu, mai aur Rajan kitne baar raat 10 tak mess khulwaye rakhte the, mess waale bhi gaali dete honge hume.
Tera jaisa carefree banda nahi dekha, 9.30 tak ke mess timing me 9.40 par breakfast karne jaana, 7 pm ke event ke liye 7.10 par room se nilakna, room par bakchodi karte karte ghar ke liye bus hi miss kar dena, jalwe to tumhare bahot rhe hai.
Bhai teri advice hamesha acchi hoti thi. Day 1 par hi tune mujhe advice di thi middle waala bed na lene ki, par maine fir bhi liya, par uske baad se samajh aa gya tha ki teri advice kaam ki hoti hai. Library me bhi mai 30% time padhta tha, aur 70% time ghumta, sota aur phone chalata, tu hi kehta tha ki padh le bc. Tu behaviour bhi kaafi acche se notice karke mistakes aur unke solution bata deta tha, kaafi help mili hai mujhe tere analysis se.
Humare bagal me rehte the Shubham aur Deepak, mast apni duniya me, bilkul chill aur fir aata tha humara kamra, hum dono hi bhaavanao me dube rehte. Aur issi wajah se Shubham ko hum dono ko har alternate day walk par leke jaana padta tha:)
Bahot ghoome hai mai, tu aur Sbhubham. Aur ghoomne ke saath saath ice cream bhi to khate the. Aur Hall 12 canteen me har weekend khaane jaate the hum teeno, uss din mess me aalu jo hota tha.
Tamonud aur Rajan ko bahot chedha bhi hai par unke saath masti bhi bahot ki hai humne. 
Aur hum dono hi aalsi the, 8-9 ghante sona, dophar me bhi soo jaana, end sem me jagna mushkil hota tha humare liye aur last paper deke aate hi neend jaane kaha gayab ho jaati thi, end sem ke exhaustion ke bavjud puri raat jaag kar ek season khatam kar dete the.
Aur 2nd aur 3rd year me hum running partners bhi to the. PE ground se start karke Director bunglow se hote hue airstrip se hokar aate the. Best track dhundha tha humne. Baarish me to lagta tha Switzerland me bhaag rhe hai.
Uske baad raat me professor's quaters waale area me cycling bhi to karne nikalte the aur uss samay kaafi gehri baatein hoti thi.
 
From being a decent singer in first year to writing, composing and singing your own songs, you have come a long way and the efforts you put in for this are commendable. The hours and hours of sheer hardwork was something not everyone can do. But then, not everyone is Dhawal Raturi.
I can't even imagine the courage it took to let go of the placements and go for your passion of being a musician. Hats off to you and I am already your fan. You are smart, talented and ready to put in the work and for that I believe you'll get everything you have set out to achieve. And when you make it up there, just get us backstage tickets for your concert:)
You are passionate and ambitious and you are gonna have a hell of a life.
I couldn't have asked for a better friend and roommate. 
I won't miss you because we'll always be in touch. 
All the best bro and I really wish you get all that you desire and still more.
author: Aditya Singh Rathore

Fir teesreaur chauthe sem me bhi humne kaafi collaborate kiya par paachve sem se to alag hi jalwe the humare, saari classes me saath baithna, class ke baad masti, lab me bakchodi, quizzes se pehle randi rona, quiz ke baad bolna, ye hagg di par agli me fod denge....bhai alag hi mauj maari hai humne saath me. 

Aur bhai terese mai bada intimidate ho jaata tha, jab jao bc padh rha hota, subha dekho, Kamboj padh rha hai, shaam me dekho, bc abhi bhi Kamboj padh rha hai. Par saale tu rota bahot hai, wo bhi matlab ka roye to baat hai, bc faaltu me rota rehta, B aa rha hai to bhi rona, saale C laake ke khush rehta tha mai!!!! 

Bhai aise hi hardwoking aur genuine rehna aur chaapte rehna.  
Milte hai jaldi hi, aur bhi aur kisse banne hai humare.

text:
You were one of the first people I met at IITK. You were always this nice guy who used to help everyone. Tu aur Shubham the raato ke Shahenshah aur bhai mujhe aati thi 11 baje ke baad neend. Tum dono ke beech waala bed leke maine ye sunishit kar liya tha ki raato ko ab mujhe bhi jagna hai. Bhai 1st semester se hi humne kafi maze kiye aur 2nd semester me saath Galaxy karke to maza hi aa gya tha, par humne mid sem ka kuch nahi padha aur jo jage the na bhai hum uske baad....

Bhai tu atyant cool hai, EDMs me tere dance moves dekh kar to DU waale ( waali I mean) bhi tere fan ho gye the, jo locks and pops maare hai tune. Kabhi bhi boldo tereko ghumne chalne ke liye, tu ready rehta tha hamesha, chahe next day exam hi kyu na ho. Bhai itna enthu aur itni energy laata kaha se tha, saale ek din me 20km kon chal leta hai, Bournvita ke saath aisa kya peeta tha?

Aur chaapu to tu hadd se zyda hai bhai, exam ke pehle party karke A laa rha, kaise!!!! 
Fir chahe CSE courses me A laana ho, Adobe me PPO lena ho ya hackathons me fodna ho, sabme tu aage. 
Aur tere Kishore Kumar, Mukesh aur Rafi ke gaane....bhai room ka radio tha tu, continous background music deta tha, mereko to kabhi kabhi aisi feel aati ki movie me hai hum aur background score chal rha hai.
And I personally feel, there couldn't have been a better CS coordinator than you. Tu ksi ke liye bhi best mentor hai.

Jaldi milte hai aur fir wapas chalte hai raat me ghoomne, kuch khane ke bahane.
author: Aditya Singh Rathore

text:
When I took the middle bed, the bed between you and Deepak, I had already made sure it was going to be hell of an interesting first year for me. From being roommates to becoming brothers, we grew up. The first time we worked together was when you, me, Deepak and Tamonud participated in Takneek, though Deepak and you did most of the work:)
We were the kings of EDMs. 'Hum chaar', you, me, Dhawal and Deepak never missed an EDM. We were always there, dancing our hearts out, doing the most insane steps. Then we used to go to Events ground . 
For sometime we were even training partners under the self acclaimed 'Best Coach' Dhanowa Sir and he made you do 200+ kg squats:) There were also some fierce badminton battles fought among us when you, me and Deepak faced each other in Room 127 badminton league.
You were always the chill one, the cool dude who never gave a fuck, or atleast that's what most people thought about you. We knew that it was just what you made others believe even though you actually cared a lot.
After Deepak was taken away from us by the Gucci gang, you, me and Dhawal became the three musketeers. Me and Dhawal were the emotional kind, one of us was always feeling low for some reason or the other. You were our saviour, our knight is shining armour, who used to say 'chalo ghumne chalte hai, chaach bhi peeyenge raaste me' and then we used to embark on your bitching journey with chaach in one hand and dark chocolate in another. 
I really enjoyed going to the gym with you, getting all that gym gyaan from you and trying to eat as many eggs as you did.
Tereko swimming bhi sikha dete par tu chala hi nahi humare saath swimming pool.
Geeky Shubham, you were the Technical Guruji for me, you were my go to person when I needed any movie link or any app or needed any help regarding my phone or laptop. 
And your love for MasterChef and anime came as a shock for me, I would have never thought you would be into cooking and anime, cause from starting you were a 'pru' gamer. I hope to see you someday in MasterChef.
You were a great roommmate and are an even better friend.
All the best and I know that you will achieve great things.
author: Aditya Singh Rathore

text:
Loki bhai............. Tu God hai bro Tu GOD hai.
Aaj tak wo aadmi hume Banarasi Babu bulata aaya hai, wo insaan jiske performance se ache se intimidate ho jae Us Interpector Vajpayee to mere Har Har Mahadev.
Bhai pata hai abhi Ostwal aur Rochak ke bhi memoirs likhe hum lekin un dono me aur tere saath meri bonding me ek bauhat major difference hai. Ostwal ke room me bakchodi hoti thi jab Drams ke kaam se khali hoke aate the sab, lekin tumhare saath tab tab bonding hoti thi jab ye sab drams ke cordinator ka bhar sambhalte the aur hum aapke saath baith ke B-bot me dhoop sekte the. 
Chahe Shakuni mama ho ya Sunil Shetty Loki ki performance ke baad kisi ki himmat nahi hoti thi ki usko follow kare.... (Nipun try kiya ... yaad hai naa kya hua tha uske saath). Aur un sab ke baad bhi tere jitna down to Earth aadmi nai dekha yaar. Tumhare life me jo ch*d hue the unke baare me tum thoda bauhat batae the lekin un sab ko overcome karke tum kaise aage badh gaye wo bhi dekhe hai hum.
Yaar bhai baaki sab se to ye keh rahe hai ki milenge phir kabhi naa kabhi lekin tumse ek waada chahiye hume... bhai tere saath Amarnath jaana hai jab tum bolo jaha bhi honge sab chod ke chalenge lekin chalenge zaroor.
Actually a fan!
Banarasi Babu
author: Aishwarya  Agrawal

text:
Haa bhai! Ostwal baaki sab to theek hai pehle ye bata.... sutts hai? Yaarrrr kya likhe teri tareef me... Yaar sach batae to kabhi soche nahi the ki TOA2 me AH Sir ki gaaliyan share karne ke baad ek din tere saath sutts share karenge aur in that process I will find one of my best friends in you.
Pata hai bro, tere determination aur kaam karne ke tareeke se day-1 se jalte the hum kyoki kitna bhi koshish kar lo wo Ostwal level ki zidd kabhi aayi hi nahi. Koi aadami summer me din bhar play me marwane ke baad bhi InterviewBit kholne ki himmat rakhe to wo bas Ostwal hi ho sakta hai.
Yaar tujhe yaad karo to wo InterIIT ki trip yaad aati hai. December ka mahina 5 degree temprature aur thanda paani. Usme Ostwal aur Rochak ka wo plan yaad aata hai ki nahate hai bc dekha jaega aur phir...... 5 min baad apne adjacent cubical se teri chillane ki aawaze yaad aati hai. Yaar tareef karna kabhi nahi aaya hume aur usko as sarcasm chupate aae hai but to be honest Nilay ke jaane ke baad tum hi wo 1 aadmi tha jisko hum personal baate bata sakte the without the risk of any leaks, chahe wo mere breakup ki baat ho ya Academic Warning ki, it was just you who I could trust it with.
Bhai itna kuch saath me dekhe hai hum log ki sirf Katiyar hi hai wo usko words me samjha sakta hai aur uske liye bhi usko ek poora gaana likhna hoga.
Aage ke liye kya hi bole, tu waise bhi kabhi room pe nahi bulata tha to abhi bhi bas khud sahi se rahiye hum tujhe aur sutts ko dhoondte party karne pauhach hi jaenge. 
Thanks Bhai

text:
First of all, teri DP me ... that's my jacket. Nana bhai tere baare me kya hi bole, Orientation yaad hai hume jab tum pehli baar "Nana" kiye the and uske baad seedhe Antaragni17 jab nukkad ke beech me sab 3-4 year ke beech me ek first year aake chaap ke chala gaya tha. Tumse zyaada shayad hi kisi ki maare ho kabhi, lekin bhai tumhe miss bauhat karenge yaar. Tu 3rd year me Nipun ke room me kam hi aata tha, volleyball me gayab rehta tha lekin uske baad bhi kitna bhi gariya le Nana ke aana se party ka mazaa badh jaata tha. 
Now I 100% agree ki humare group me most probably I was the one wo sabse zyaada maara hai tumhari, chahe wo IIT Roorkee me sube sube tumhare gayab hone pe tumhari maarna ho ya uske bas 1 hi din baad zabaradasti tumse poore Y17 ko treat dilwana lekin yaar in sab me sorry nahi bol rahe hum kyoki tu tha yaar, nana mast aadmi hai isiliye to ye sab ar lete the nana ke saath isiliye to aaj se 2 saal pehle tere saath photo khichwae the ye soch ke ki ye to As we leave ka portrait hoga.
Tum un logo me ho jo abhi kuch din aur campus ki shobha badhenge to tum to chinta mat karo aate rahenge kam se kam 1 saal aur aapke maze lene aur aapke saath legend level ka Volleyball khelne.
Maze me rehna bro nana ki bakchodi kabhi kam nahi honi chahiye.
.......

Ohh fuckk, I almost forgot to talk about that nighttt........ uske bina ye memoir complete hi nahi ho sakta.... Yaar me Has Kyu raha ho. Wo raat jab Piyush Sunil Samartha ko Alan aur Rochak first time me poora joint phhokwa diye the aur Nana meri bas ek line "Suffering from Success" pe pehle 1 ghanta hasa aur phir 1 ghanta roya tha.... Bhai aaj tak kisi ko pata nahi us din tere dimaag me kya chal raha the. Aur bhai agli baar aae to yaad rakhna phir se wo OAT waali photo khichwaenge.
author: Aishwarya  Agrawal

text:

Tum chapu aadmi ho yaar, I know bauhat garyae hai tumhe bauhat lade hai lekin un sab me pata tha ki kitna bhi gariya lo Ratnedha Argal apne kaam aadha nahi chodega.

Thanks yaar for everything you are one of the most patient people I know. Jaldi milte hai dost

text:
oyy yaarr... chalo naa.... Bas yahi aata hai Rochak Dindor ke baare me socho to yahi sabse pehle yaad aata hai. Hands down the most fun person I knew in campus. Kitna bhi kharaab mood ho kitni bhi serious baat ho Rochak Dindor can take any topic and make it about chal m**l maarte hai bc.
Although Aasman Gir Raha Hai me saath me the lekin I got to know the real Dindor during the brief practice of NSS nukkad. Kaala chasma lagae full swag me TS karta hua, itna ziddi ki nukkad khatam hone ke baad bhi apna 4-liner bol ke hi gaya.
Iske baad tumse dosti hui Summer me, Jab Aayush Ostwal was the Prop manager aur hum dono unke atyacharo se pareshaan hoke usko gariyate the aur in the end lad ke hi sahi kaam kar lete the. Also how can I forget Rochak DIndor the bad cop..... The most fun guy turned into a bad cop kyoki usi me to asli fun hai. Kedia se inspire hoke wo bachho ki maari thi ki hum dono bilkul opposite reasons se drameve-1 me bachon ke beech popular ho gaye the.
Abhi thodi der pehle KT ke memoir me tune likha tha ki Varun ka Sarcasm Aishwarya se kam hai.... honoured but I have a similar comparison to make...... Nana kitni bhi koshish karle Rochak ki bakchodi kabhi match nahi kar paega.
Saale tum msgs ke end me alvida to likh rahe ho lekin jaan lo ki tum officer ban jao chahe Pradhan Matri sutta lene tumhe hi phone karenge hum. Aur naa tumhe bhoolne denge kyoki jo scenes specially 2nd year Antaragni me apan milke banae the uske baad we are crime mates forever.
Bhai bauhat kuch hai tere baare me kehne ko to lekin ....... ab man nahi hai! Aapki shayari aur Ostwal ke liye innovative innovative gaaliyan sunne ka bada man karta hai..
Badalna mat be aur maa mat ch**ana kabhi milne ko bole to..
Baaki to Dindori baba zindabad hai the aur rahenge. Har Har Mahadev
author: Aishwarya  Agrawal

text:
Varun Jain ....... Yaar pata hai Drameve-1 me to utni nahi hui thi tumse bonding but NSS nukkad me jo Varun Jain ki image thi mere man me wo thi, an not very hard to convince guy who is barely comfortable in the circle but boyyyyyy was I wrong. Us NSS nukkad ke baad 3 saal almost continously tumhare saath the and I saw the most strong willed person I know, Y17 to chodo Y16 waale bhi 2 log aate the baaki sab to batana aur baaki 2 jaate the Varun Jain ko manane. Also, you were the most comfortable person I ever saw in the circle. Hume yaad hai hum, tum aur Nipun gaye the dram treat ke liye paise lene aur koi bola tha tumse ki tum same tatti itni confidently kar kaise lete ho......
Itne performances kiye apan saath me chahe wo tumhara legendary role as Jamal (ya fazlu) ho ya the super legendary performance as Assistant Director Hamlet ho but apni bonding kaha hui ye shayad hume, tumhe aur Barwal ko hi pata hoga. IIT Roorkee ke wo mess ke chakkar yaar, those were the best times ever.
Yaar itnii memories hai ki kya kya batae, tera wo anokha negotiation at Dram Treat ya handling both Y18 and Y16 with the same attitude. I seriously I'll ever come across some one as relaxed as you. And ofcourse, this memoir would be incomplete without talking about the longest running credential in both of ours life.... Sexist Hall 12 + Aishwarya. Yaar aaj us baat ko 2 saal se zyaada ho gaye lekin abhi tak nahi samajh aaya tu kiya kya tha..... Mera to hume yaad hai that I was the one jo pehli chingaari diye the but tera aaj tak nahi pata. Y17 Fakr Hai,
A fellow Sexist

You are a natural leader. You inspire me to work harder.
TA201 me mai raat bhar night-out maarke thakke aata tha, aur fraud hi maarta tha mai. But I was assured ki tum hoge, to sambhaal loge, aur mereko push karoge. ESC201 me jis jis din vo lab partner (mere se bada fraudi tha wo) aata nahi, us din tum mera partner bann jate the. Thanks yaar.

"à´•à´¿à´³à´¿ à´ªàµ‹à´¯à´¿"

Bruh I could say you changed my life, but that wouldn't be the whole truth. The changes go deeper than the layers which constitute "me". There were so many irrelevant things I stupidly clung to with my pig-headed rationalism until you took my hand and helped me leave them behind in those cleansing hot waters (you know which one). I still remember thinking "wtf is he talking about" when you first unleashed all that non-duality stuff on me. I would never even have seriously taken to watching films if it weren't for you. If I made a film of all the things we did, it would be more surreal than Lynch, more outrageous than Rivette, and more spiritual than Tarkovsky. Your imprint is all over me.

And, yeah, you are THE ARTIST, bro. And not all of your art is paint and sketches - one of those artworks is a living breathing computer nerd. And may I be brash for once to say, that you (as always) have made a MASTERPIECE.

text: â€œAaj to kahi chal le yaarâ€. Tujhe shanti hi nhi rehti thi bhai kabhi, roz kahi chalo. Par agar ye attitude na hota to itna ghum hi nhi paate. Koi trip tere bina imagine hi nhi kar sakta main bhai. Delhi ho ya Goa ya Rishikesh ya Shimla, par ye to bas shuruat hai aane waale time ki jab trip pe trip padhti raha karegi. Orchha hi reh gaya yaar end tak, par waha to solo trip hi maar le. You are the nicest person I met in the campus, aur arrangement me expert. Music ka arrangement, light ka arrangement, kuch bhi party-related bolo to ho jaaye. CCD se kab Anaichaâ€™s hua aur kab Goa pata hi nhi chala. Wo accident yaad hai na jab Abhishek hospital gaye the. Aur wo maal ke baad thand lagna, jisne poori raat kharaab kar di thi. Topa chori ho gaya tha bhai par aisi 100 raatein kurbaan hai. Wo din bhi acche se yaad hai jab jab roye hai kisi baat ko lekar, especially college khatam hone ke. But these things aside, mujhe life me kabhi bhi kuch kaam padhega to sabse pehla phone tujhe hi jayega bhai. First year Antaragni ke condoms se leke wo bahut dur ke open mic se leke final year ki aakhri party tak sab kuch saath kiya hai bhai. Itne saare nightouts maare hai, RM tak ko nhi chhoda bhai. Itni bets lagayi hai, vaccine waali to bachi hai abhi aur books waali bhul mat jaana â€œheheâ€. Wo video to safe rhega mere pass most probably. I could say anything I want to you. Meethi si wo gaali teri sunne ko tayyar hu main. Honestly speaking, I will wish for a friend like you wherever I go, aur kya hi bolu bhai.

text: Khushkismati hai ye meri ki tere jaisa panauti aadmi meri life me aaya. First year se kaafi hangout karta tha tu ground floor pe and that was the best thing that could have happened. Bol bol ke thak gaya tha Bechara ki coding karne chalo koi saath me, akela karke aa jaata tha dhokebaaz. Bahut annoying aur irritating aadmi hai yaar tu par kabhi mat bhulna â€œSonu, tune humre pe bharosa kahe nai ke.â€ Itna sehen karne ke saath saath kitne to assignment kiye hai yaar. Aur har course ke saath kuch na kuch incident hai, jaise â€œye O hai ya 0â€. CS220 to tu mere bina nikal hi nhi pata, power cable to maine hi connect ki thi humesha :sunglasses:. Galaxy waala poora sem to tere upar hi chhod diya tha. Tu agar na hota to aaj kasam se degree nhi nikalti. Cannot imagine college without you. Aise helpful log bahut kam hote hai duniya main par apne baare me thoda to sab hi sochte hai. Itna entertain kiya hai first year se apni marwake, I am astonished. Chaar log khade ho aur saath me tu ho to aur kisi ki maarte hi nhi hai log, kuch special effect hai ye tera. But that is because people love you, cutest Y17 male hai bhai tu wo bhi aisi shakal ke saath, hidden compliment hai ye. Altu faltu ki cheezein bhi bahut mangwayi hai tune, kabhi dab karta hua penguin to kabhi use and throw stuff. Ek baat ka dukh hai par first time mere saamne nhi gaali baki tune lodu. Zindagi me kabhi bhi code nhi likhayega to tere pass hi aaunga, bada aadmi banke bhul mat jaana Noogler. Bahut Maria milti rhe tujhe aur gaanja bhi milta rhe, yehi duaa karunga.
author: Anany  Sharma

text: Waise to we are from the same city, but we came here as acquaintances. We got into a petty fight and then one walk changed everything. I have got many defining moments from being with you and learnt a lot about life. You broaden my perspective. I have had 21 birthdays till now, but no one did anything special compared to what you did, you made me feel special that day with your excellent craft skills. Delhi ki wo trip humesha yaad rhegi, but the best time would undoubtedly be the time we spent in Mumbai. I hope you remember the horse ride. But above the big things in life, I value the small things we had, especially the painting of minions which I had to complete as you were not that good a painter. And also, the little notes you used to leave for me at unexpected places. It was a new experience for me to be in a relationship and I realised that it was the thing that was missing because I got you, you completed my life in the campus. Fire department ke saath waala incidence to main kabhi nhi bhulunga, aur na hi marine drive pe wo baithna, jaha aisa laga ki waqt ruk hi jaata to achha hota. Kaafi competitive spirit hai tujhme jo lifelong maintain rakhna hai (in a healthy way *wink*). We spent a lot of time in many different places. Kabhi RM, kabhi library, kabhi GH, but the best was the skywalk, and a close second is the Earth Science building. Wo road bhi achhi hai jo library se RM tak jaati hai. I respect you for the progress you have made since the first year. Poori journey kaafi achhi rahi but I still wish we had met earlier and got more time in the campus. Call me when you want, call me when you need. text:
Tere jitna lamba memoir nahi likh paaunga, itni BT 1 din m handle nhi hogi!
First we met in the triple room, aur tumne kaha tha â€œmein bahubaliâ€. We were the only â€œaero guysâ€ in the wing. Tumse bheek mangta tha ki mere liye ruk jana HSS ke baad kyunki mujhe TA101 ki lab ka rasta yaad nahi tha (aaj bhi nahi h)!

Pehlie antaragni m bandi search kar rahe the saath m, tumhare baap se tips bhi li thi, but jab end m kuch nhi hua to saath m raat bhar pura campus ghume the saari raat!
Yaad h wo first year endsem ki raat hum poore campus m ghum rahe the padne ki jagah ke liye, jab hum apne â€œbhutiyaâ€ departmental building gaye the!
â€œ2 days exercise krta hu to pett andar ho jata hâ€, â€œjo ladkiyo se baat krte h wo virgin nahi hoteâ€, â€œJab fever aaye to khelna chahiye, fever chale jata hâ€, I said m covid +ve hu you said â€œtheek hai, apna trimmer de janaâ€!
Esse na jane kitne â€œspecialâ€ statements bataye h tumne!
Kotana se kitni treats nikali h humne, dabbe ki, uske charge ki, pre-birthday treat! LOL!
You said ki â€œGraduate hone ke baad hi peena shuru karunga!â€, LOL!

You worked hard in the aeromodelling club, from summer project to secy, from secy to cordi!
Fir life m ek nibbi aayi jisne tumhare raato ki neend aur din ka chain udaa diya!
Tumne uske liye sabke against jaake secy banaya, took care of here, (expensive) gifts diye!
Padne ka mann nahi hota tha exams ke time, usko uthane ke liye khud subah jaldi uthte the tum!
Aur hua kya â€¦ L*** lagye gaye! Oooooo! L*** lag gayeeeee! LMAO!
Double katwaya h tumne, but important life lesson de gayi wo!

Humne Sacred Games ka second season puri raat binge watch kiya tha!
Humne GOT season 8 ka pura saath dekha h, jo bekar tha!
Placements ke wo stressful moments, jab lagta tha ki placement hi nahi lagegi!

Placement hone ke baad to saatve asmaan pe the sab, sabko tips baat rahe the!

2 baar covid +ve bande ke MOST PRIMARY contact hone ke baad bhi kuch nahi hua, apne blood se vaccine banao, named â€œBahubaliâ€.
End m hum 32 days campus m aaye the, jisme 22 days m quarantine tha, but those 10 days were the best days of my college!

author: Atharv  Tyagi

text:
"AVVIIIIIIIIIIRAAAAAAALLLLLLLLLLLLLL!!!" fuck, that was scary. Never thought that we would be friends but oh god we did. Do you remember all those evil vibes of competition we used to give me (tedhi nazre)? Started from a casual hello in TA lab, ended with a goodbye hug (oh, and that imli too xP). It was definitely a great journey with a lot of highs and lows (still sorry for that 5th sem ki overthinking). You can proudly say that you were the one behind showing me some places on campus that are not supposed to be visited. The only GH visit was to your room (mudreka kya chutiyo ki tarah kha raha tha uss din). 
I never thought a girl would hit so hard during my birthday GPL but TU JANWAR HAI. Also, vo dumbbell shaped bottle dope thi. When I look back, I feel proud of our friendship. All those discussions where we came to know each other a lot better. You are rare, that's a fact, varna how watches the videos of beheading someone and making a football out of it (MF Psycho xD!!). 
Well, what I know about you and how I've known you is a lot different from what people say about you. If Google ever plotted the data of personalitites of their employees, you would be that outlier! 
Take care, we'll stay in touch for sure.

Yo Mallu (and my birthday twin)!! If I ever made the right decision in college, it was choosing you as my roommate. Itna ideal kaise ho sakte ho bhaaii!
To this date as well, I hate those memories of your early morning coffee ke nashe and then subah subah pooja karke, you used to give me prasad in sleep. I was an idiot to mention this to my parents and I still get scoldings to be like you. Never had I ever seen someone actually use an alarm that requires you to solve math puzzles to snooze off. One thing that I missed the most was your shoulder massages (bhai bhai). I never feared about missing my breakfast because of you and even when I missed it, you used to bring me sprouts. Wing ki maaa tha tu. Oh and how can I forget forcing you into girls, lolol.
You are some sort of a weird person in yourself but we missed you during the last days. All the very best for anything you aspire to achieve. D111 will be our room!!

Hello, Deepak/Dipak/Dipuk (a confusion which is going to stay a long time). 
We met through CS and I will always be thankful to CS for this friendship. You make everyone around you comfortable, people who know you absolutely love you including me. Thank you for equalizing all my emo-boy shayaris with your great ones and thank you for all the value you brought to our team. You were truly a blessing to the team.

text:
Oh, tune public kar diya finally. If I wanted, I could have DM'd you but jane do kya hi yaad rakhoge. Tere jaise ghatiya dost toh kisiko na hi mile. kyu hi dost hai hum?!

That said, tu kaafi mast admi hai. I'm not gonna lie, tu billy jaise dikhte lol. tera harkate bhi waisa hi hai. Thank God kabhi kata nahin. Baaki toh tareef karne se tu udne lagega so woh nahin karunga. Oh haan, shaadi mai bulana zaroor. And mai kabhi Assam aya toh bridge pe photoshoot ke liye ja sakte.

Thanks for being a great friend over the years. I wonder what would have become of me if it weren't for your constant and unwavering support. Countless hours of pointless cycling just because I wanted to, and midnight talks at OAT are something I'll remember for quite some time. The last I checked, you owe me a few chocolates so you better send them soon.

text:
Yo bitch, well I had to think A LOT of what to write, but then thought that I should just start writing :)
We've been through so much that it's hard to condense it all into a memoir (Also, given my remembering power, lol).
I remember meeting your mom the very first day at Hall 3, and later coming over to your room, seeing you there, sitting on the bed without mat in a corner. I had no idea that we'd be bonding soo well.
Those long hours of binge watching shows together with lights off to get the cinematic feels, playing games together, bitching and laughing at every fucking thing! Those pizza king (or king of pizza) maina orders we ate, then when we couldn't finish it, trying to find anyone who could lol. Yaad hai voh RM mein poora din pade rehte the, especially during summers. Oh bhai, this is really nostalgic. I was really lucky to have such an awesome friend, brother and roommate.
You really are my brother from another mother!
Keep up those positive vibes and that one hell of a confidence man. May you reach everything you aim for in future.
PS. Covid khatam hote hi Ahmedabad aa rha mein, for sure.
Bye until then.
Take care bro.
Cheers!

text:
Bhai tu yaaro ka yaar hai. 
Same coaching se the. Coaching mai ek baar ladai bhi kar li thi. Fir bhi jab hum orientation mile muje bilkul yaad nahi tha tu kaun hai. Muje toh uss waqat aisa tha ki tujse pehli baar mil raha hu.
Yeh kissa toh tum dono mai se koi kabhi nahi bhulne wala. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚ Jab bhi hum dono kisi aur se milenge tu yeh usko batae bina nahi rehne wala. As always I will be like bhai ab kya karu mai. 

Uncle Ji ke ghar firse Diwali par jarur chalenge.
Mere saare bhaiyo se alag alag jagah mila tha. Jab tu pehli baar humare room par aya tha toh. Literally tuje toh haar 2 min mai shock mil raha tha. You were like - Yeh bhi tera bhai hai? Yeh bhi tera bhai hai? ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

Agar kisi ka BDay aata tha aur tere paas agar uski photo nahi hoti thi. Toh tu sabse pehle uski photo ka jugad karta tha. Uske baad uss photo ko upload karke BDay wish karta tha.

Finally kafi mehnate insaan hai tu. Thoda dara hua bhi rehta hai. Aage apna kya hoga. 
Muje jitna yaad hai backlog toh teri sirf ek course mai hi ayi thi. Vo course mai teesari baar kar raha hu. Abhi bhi pata nahi iss baar bhi niklega ya nahi. Padhta tu regular tha. Saat mai shayad fail ho sakte hai vo daar thoda constant tha tera. 
Tere no/cpi dekh kar tere ghar walo ko lagta hoga. Bilkul padhta likhta nahi hai. Par tuje pata hai aur muje bhi pata hai mehnat mai tune kahi koi kami nahi rakhi hai. Ab relative grading mai no nahi aate toh vo toh apne haat mai nahi. 

Ek baar tu EE250A ki quiz se pehle muje NCL mai mila tha. Maine kuch bhi padh nahi rakha tha. Bode plot tune muje itna aache se samjhaya tha ki mai aaj tak nahi bhula hu. Par tu khud bhul gaya tha. Mid sem mai ussi NCL mai muje tuje samjhana pada tha. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

TA ka project poora kaise uski poore grp mai sabse jyada chinta tuje thi. Uss sem tu grp mai kisi se bhi milta toh TA project ka poochta tha. Kisi koi idea nahi hota tha kya chal raha hai. Par haar koi kisi aur ka naam leh kar bol deta tha. Vo toh kar hi raha hoga. Tu chill maar ho jayaga. Finally katam ho toh gaya tha. ğŸ˜‚ğŸ˜‚

Finally itna bata raha hu ki tu jitni mehnat karta hai usse ek bahut aachi jagah pauch jayaga. Abhi tuje kafi daar lag raha hoga aage apna kya hoga. But thoda chill maar. Badiya hi hoga. All the Best.

text:
Hey Bro,
I met you for the first time via the Electronics Club and then we prepared for the Engineers Conclave in winter '18. I still remember us struggling to find the display room for the project in IITB :P. You were always so helpful and I remember thinking to myself as to how much you know. Then, we did the TA202A project. I remember us bitching about the team members we ended up with but still getting through the course somehow. ESO203 lab was a nightmare, figuring out which wire went where and invariably us finishing our lab work last before getting to know that the rest of the groups used to cheat :P. The last semester in AML you really helped me bro, I didnt know anything and you literally covered for me so much. I hope I wasn't too much of a burden. I would always cherish your friendship Bro. Always be like this, never change. Hope we stay in contact. 
Wish you a great life ahead.

Bahgwaan kare tere jaisa roommate kisi ko na mile, kitna ganda rakhta hai room bsdk.
Tere jaisa multitasker maine kabhi dekha nahi tu harr kaam dil laga ke karta hai, SAE,  semester, GYM , squaash , bhollyball, etc etc. 
Kitna kanjoos hai tu be bsdk ek treat nikalwaane mein gaand mar jaati thi,  kabhi kabhi mann hota tha raat ko sote hue pel doon tere ko.
Puraani baaten yaad karta hoon to tera bhollyball ke smaaaash, canteen mein tera randirona, logon ke cheezen cheen ke khana, aur galaxy mein tera almaa dolmaa , ye sab yaad aata hai. Tere saath rahte rahte teri aadat si gayi thi mujhe sala ghar pe jab sota hoon to lagta hai abhi subah uthte hi aaishi ki baddi sakal dekhni padegi, raat mein jab batti jala ke padhta hoon to lagta jai abhi aaishi bhosdiwala light band karne ko bolega. First year mein yaad hai tujhe gaali theek se dena nahi aata tha madarchod ki jagah madarchut bolta tha , gaali dena bhi maine hi sikhaya hai.

Tu waise to bahut productive hota hai lekin ladki ke chakkar mein tu bahut chutiya ban jata hai, jab bhi teri aur Ashreeta ki kahani yaad karta hoon tere chutiyaape ka khayaal aata hai .

text:
Pandey yaar 
Chaddhi king , maza aata tha tujhe chaddhi mein dekh ke, aise hi chaddhi mein ghoomte rahna, last mein maze bhut kiya bhai, Tune bowling mein bahut improve kiya wo bhi do hafte mein itna jaldi seekhte hue kisi ko nahi dekha maine, tere ko peetna bahut kathin ho gaya tha last tak, aur bsdk madarchod gandu lawde mera hi wicket kyon leta tha bsdk, poore din main sochta tha ki aaj chakke peeloonga pandey ko sala ek chakka hi maar pata tha.
Aur tere se mujhe paise wasoolna seekhna hai, saala koi bhi wapas hi nahi karta. Kabhi kabhi to aisa ho gaya tha ki avinash ke paise lage hain matlab nahi dena hai.
Tu ek field main improve kar sakta hai ki, maze karne ka intezzar nahi karte, ye soch ke nahi baithete ki kuch ban jaaonga fir maze karoonga, dekho jo kuch bhi hai abhi hai isliye usse khul ki jeeyo kyon ki kal kisne dekha . Jiase ki ho sakta tha last mein hame buaate hi nahi to kya hota koi maza naa ho pata.
Baaki pandey tu hai dil kaa saaf aadmi aur jeevan mein kai mukaan haasil karega , jald hi milenge tu to pass ka hi hai , teri shaadi mein naagin dance karege saali waali kidnap kar loonga.

P.S.- Tera ladikyon ko lekar jo approach hai wo mast hai aise hi bajate raho lekin vivaah hone ke baad kuch kiya to tere biwi ko sab bata doonga fir uska kandha ban jaaonga aur aage ki kahani to tu jaanta hi hai (no body no body  no body .......... does it better).

text:
Priye Bhrata Ankit 
Kahan se suru karoon bahut jyada baaten hain. First year mein dono saath mein padhna suru kiye wahan se achhi dosti suru ho gayi , tu wing ke neeche khada hoke jab mera naam pukaarta tha to behenchod poora wing jaan jata tha , hum dono ka naam galat tareeke se joda jana laga.kaise din raat NCL mein chudaate the fir doaa canteen jaake gaand marwaate the aur aisa karte karte aavishkaar hua maa chudaane waale Shaashtra ka. Aur apni dasti aur bhi pakki tab hui jab hame pata chala ki hum dono ka dil ek hi apsara pe hai . Kiase dono saath mein milke uski sundarta ka varnan karte the , kabhi kabhi sochta tha ki engineering chhod ke sayar ban jaaon aur sirf ussi ke liye likhoon. 2nd year taak aate aate  jab hum poori tarah se niraas ho gaye the tab aaviskaar hua BUS theory ka. Pata nahi kyon tere har baat share karna kitna aasan lagta tha. Peeche mud ke dekhta hoon to tere ko wing se nikaalne ka bhut dukh hota hai mere ko and I feel more sad when I realize ki main tujhe wing mein daal sakta tha mere paas authority thi fir bhi pata nahi kyon nahi kiya main. Main Parag  aur tu mere ko ek trio jaisa feeling aata tha jisme main comfortable feel karta tha, aur hum log sab milke dabba aur phone banwaane jaate the aur sirf wahi kaam karke aate the(kaisa laga mera mazak) . Aur teri dard bhari kahaniyaan jo tu bahut khoobi ke saath sunata tha I feel sad for every girl jo tujhe jaan nahi paayi ki tu heera hai bsdk.

P.S. -IAS ban ke jis ladki se shaadi karna uski koi bahiya si bahen ya cousin jarror honi chahye aur usse mere liye book karke rakhna.

text:
Priye Bhrata Sharma
Galaxy mein tujhse mulaaakaat hui aur wahan se jo dosti bani wo amar ho gayi hai. 
Sabse pahli baat teri aawaj aur bolne ka lahza bahut mast hai tere ko bolte hue sunne main babut maza aata tha, lakin kabhi kabhi tark mein bolte waqt jo tu chehre ke expressions banata tha naa usse dekh mujhe aur Harshit ko bahut maza aata tha. Tera bina practice kane mein bilkul maza nahi tha .
Fir aate hain dumbc pe uske to kya hi kahne main tark karte karte marr jata agar hum log last mein dumbc ki practice na karte , dumbc hi tha jisne hamara aapas ka bond aur seniors(akshit , ji prakhar ji, Thoury, Sampat , Sudhaanhu) se bhi badhaya, Dumbc hi kaaran tha ki hamara harr practice happy note pe khatam hota tha. Main ligos kabhi nahi bhoolonga mainre apne wing waalon ko bhi sikha diya last ke months mein aur ushe bhi bahut maza aaya.
Tum last mein milne nahi aa paaye uska hisaab alag se dena padega meri adalat mein jahan judge, vakeel, gawah aur dandnayak sab main hi hoon.
I wish tu meri wing mein rahta hota bahut gaand marate saath mein.
Tune ek baar bola tha jab hum budhdhe ho jaayenge aur alumni meet hoga to aayegi aur tu sabke samne mujhe kaluva bulaaega, well I am waiting for that day, lekin wo to bahut door ki baat hai, fir se jald hi milenge mere Kota mein kuch hissab kitaab baaki hain aur wo Do anmol ratan bhi to wahi hain (Waise do nahi ek hi hai, apne year ki).

P.S.-waise to dhoodh ki rakhwaali ke liye billi rakhna bewkoofi hai lekin fir bhi tere upar bharosaa kar raha hoon Kota ka wo anmol ratan tere bharose chhod raha hoon.

text:
Jab bhi humari baat hogi to Sainik School sabse pehle aayega. Jo bond 2 Sainik school vaalon ke beech me ho sakta hai vo normally nahi hota. Starting from the PHY101 lab jahan hum lab partners the, baaki log values nikal ke graph banate the aur answers nikalte the, Vahi hume reverse pattern follow krte the. Pehle answer aur uske baad values manipulate krte the. PHY101 ki first lab me hi TA se mera ladai krna and all. Vahan se jo bond develop hua vo aaj usse kahi jyada strong hai. text:
Alright! As promised, I'll start with you. I hope this thing has a word limit because it will be difficult to judge the point at which you'll stop reading and just call to ask what I have to say. Linear Algebra might've been the worst course that we had to endure, but it was also the one where we actually met for the first time. It was a strange yet perfect time for us to have become friends. Well, partly because that allowed you to steal Nutella on my birthday, but mostly because I needed someone to not judge me at the time. Somehow, I always felt safer with you. Sorry, I forgot your birthday that year, but I made up for it, so you cannot complain! You were the silver lining in my life when everything was bleakâ€”someone who was always welcoming with a warm hug.

I still count our 4th semester as one of the best times I've had here, and it had a lot to do with you. From Psychology classes to TA lab shenanigans to binging Netflix to relishing our amazingly similar food tastes at god knows how many cafes to our 6 am walks (Trust me, I can't get up at 6!). The list never ends; we had good times. There are so many days where I recall you being in my corner, sometimes even going out of the line to support and stand up for me. The summer of 2019 will always be one of the highlights of our friendship; how I would look forward to us talking almost every day. I felt heard, and that is the best feeling there is. I don't think we had many differences at any point in time; however, we did get busy in our own different ways. Despite that, I'm glad that we've only grown closer and fonder with time. I hope our friendship is here to stay. 

Oh well, I think it's impossible to list all the million different reasons why you're an absolute gem of a person. Ugh, I wish I could say it all. I am proud of what you have achieved and in awe of the perseverance you possess. Also, It wouldn't kill to let the world see that you're a kind and sweet soul! But then, you know your worth. World is a mess right now, stay safe and stay healthy you moron! 

Anyway, just know that I have appreciated you every single day of our friendship. Aaah, I'll miss you a lot. Before I end this, I would like to apologise if I did you wrong intentionally or otherwise. Goes without saying that Iâ€™ll always be here for you, for better or for worse.  

Thank you for my first Mclaren. Thank you for the matchmaking XD. And well, Thank you for everything. 

PS: We'll always be Netflix buddies, and don't you dare leave!
PPS: Never stop sharing dead baby jokes!

Par tu sab chiz ke saath kaafi humble bhi hai. Mujhe abhi bhi yaad hai, humne 2 non-veg pizzas mangaye the, and usne galti se ek veg de diya tha but tune wo wala le liya. text: Munmun, Haga, Harshaga, no matter what we call you, you'll always be the bubbly, cheerful, smiling guy I know. From dancing to searching research internships (remember going to senior dorms late night fishing for advice ğŸ˜…), preparing for interviews (which I screwed up sadly ğŸ˜ª), collaborating in assignments and quizzes, NLP project, CS610 (we set a new benchmark for collaboration and bitching together ğŸ˜›) and the Goa Trip, we have been together through all these times. aur bhai nareda kaise ho...tumhara memoir socha tha pehle likhne ka par free aaj hua aur fursat mai likhna tha....kaafi sara hoga waise likhne ka so aalas....anyway here it is....tumhe pehle jana tha toh pata chala ki chillness knows no boundaries....pehli identity - gamer, ameer, chilled guy.....phir second year se toh tum ek dum mere bakchodi partner ban gaye...kahi bhi jana tumhara saath kuch bhi kaam nahi toh aa gaye tumhara room bahut bakchodi ki hai bhai kitni ginaye...wo saath mai hunter hunter phir 12:00 se 12:02 tak happy new year...wo delhi ka safar bus se (adventure with death)...woh bombay ki trip...kaafi saath raha hai second sem se hi...saath mai canteen jana tumhara paiso pe :'), beete mahine bhi bas hum dono hi the jo har waqt free rehte the tumhara saath rehte rehte mai bhi free ho gaya....baaki goa trip pe na aane ka dukh hai par koi na ummed hai ki aage aur bhi trips saath mai hongi...likhte likhte mujhe abhi porn discussion at sahil room yaad aa gya :), bhai bahut time saath gujara hai maja aaya milte rehna #AllTheBest #Bhai #BakchodiPartner
Keep in mind - you are a bad boi doing bad things....aur kya likhe...ek achi baat - tu judge nahi karta logo ko aur karta hai toh maje mai uda deta hai #Relatable....ab toh apna bhai bhi bandi wala ho gaya...#MeALoner....Anyways, likhe likhte kaafi incidents recall hue wo vikram ki trip cawnpore mai paisa wo ghumta hua hotel..aise toh khatam nahi hongi par that was a good time..#WellSpentDays
Milte hai kabhi jab bhi yeh covid restriction hate..baaki koi trip ka plan bane toh batayeiga zaroor

text:
In our first year, we'd cycle back together late every night- remember? At the T-fork, I'd turn left towards Hall-5, and say "chol, kaal dekha hobe". You'd grumble a "hmmm". I've loved my time at IITK, and that notion was rooted largely in that assurance-- that I'd have a friend in you, to talk to the next day, or any day thereafter. 
Paths, of course, diverge: life doesn't seem to be too warm to the concept of "happily ever after"! There have been times I wished we continued hanging out more, that we hadn't grown into the comfort of separate lives. But we never really did, did we? Each time I pick up the phone to text you (which, as I've come to accept, will only grow more infrequent over time), I still have that feeling that I'm writing to someone who fundamentally knows me for who I am. If I can retain one thing from our time together, I'd want it to be that feeling. 
From the time we first met on a late August afternoon, in the OAT, to the last walk we shared on campus (an early April evening, almost four years later), I'll treasure each moment we hung out, talked, laughed, and sympathised with each other. Even if time flies, I truly believe we made quite a lot out of it. :) Thanks for being there to hear about my loves and my heartbreaks, my wins and my losses. I'll always be grateful to have known you, and to have been a part of your life. 
Needless to say, I fully expect you to do awesome things in life. I hope that you have a great, great time ahead: you're a really good person, and you deserve every bit of joy! 
Let's meet up soon? :)
author: Bashirul Islam Sheikh

text:
Hi. :)
I just replied to your text: sorry for the delay! :D And I'm not at all happy at the social-reciprocation-obligation you've thrust on me by writing that sweet little memoir. Or maybe I am delighted-- I'm getting a chance to write about me (well, partly :P)!
Thanks for putting up with my antics and my disappearances, for being there each time I've needed a friend (except for all the times you haven't picked up the phone :P), and for all the treats the future-you is about to give the future-me. 
In our countless hours of dissecting life, you've proven to be a phenomenally understanding listener-- and utterly, truly mad, but let's leave that aside for the moment-- and you've shown me how much you're willing to accept and change, for the sake of those that you care about. You have this crazy/amazing way of inspiring confidence and independence in those around you, and I'm eternally thankful for that (not that I myself needed any :P). 
If you ever apply to be a saint (is that a thing?), hit me up for an LoR. Although it'll be difficult to come up with anything nice about you, I'll try to.. :P And guess what-- I'll leave out the trysts with alcohols and cannabinoids too! ;) 
Also, let's go a bit easy on the crushes for now, shall we? :P
P.S.: Make the trip happen!
author: Bashirul Islam Sheikh

text:
first year ki antaragni se saath hain aur mujhe lagta hain zindagi ke aakhri din tak saath hi rahenge . itna pyar hai tujhse ki lafzon mein bayan nahi kiya ja sakta . mujhe chaar saal mein sirf ye regret hai ki galaxy ke 1 mahine mein time spend nahi kar paye hum log . you have taught me more than you will ever realise .
you will always be the coolest guy in the room because of your wittiness and humour.
mera sweater sambahl ke rakhna
author: Bhavay  Bukkal

text:
mere chote se pyare se paikrao, jab teri job lagi thi to bohot zyada khushi huyi thi mujhe . interIIT ki practise ke baad tere room mein G.O.T dekhte the  , phir ek din thand mein tune mujhe kambal nahi diya tha aur mujhe bukhar ho gaya tha aur practise pe panda mujhe daant raha tha ki bimaar kaise ho gaya . jitna bhola hai usse kahin zyada tharki hai tu . good things come in small packages , tu proper example hai is baat ka . your meme collection is out of this world , kabhi kabhi zyada hi dark ho jaate hain XD . tu aur rana dil ke bohot kareeb hain . bohot saara paisa kamao ,khoob maze karo zindagi mein .

love bhavay
author: Bhavay  Bukkal

text:
" kisan uth ja tere khet mein paani bhar gaya hai " - DEEPENDRA YADAV(antaragni 2018).
tum college ke sabse suljhe huye aur saaf dil ke insaan ho , isliye sab tumhe itna pyar karte hain . sabse zyada tu hi janta hai mere baare mein kyunki tu logon ko bina judge kare unka opinion sunta hai  , that's why you are a great leader . itni acchi baatein hain tere baare mein ki book likh dun poori . tune bohot himmat di thi mujhe antaragni karne ke liye aur bhi kaafi cheezon mein support kiya hai , i will always be indebted to you for that . kitna hard working , disciplined aur genuine hai bhai tu .tujhe kabhi dost banane ki zarurat nahi padi kyunki pehli mulaqat se BHAI tha tu mera .
agli baar milenge to movie night zaroor karenge wo bhi horror wali.
AAKASH RAWAT , THIS WORLD IS A BETTER PLACE BECAUSE OF YOUR PRESENCE .

Orientation mein jab pehli baar lollipop pe naache the tab hi pata lag gaya tha ki ye kahani lambi chalegi . galaxy mein hum teeno sabse pehle aake battle ki practise karte the aur fir group dance ki practise ke liye sabko room se bulake late the . freshers antaragni mein select huye the to kya naache the dance room mein ,freshers mein bhi saath mein the apan dono . haarna aur jeetna dono saath mein dekha hai . campus aa jata bhai bohot maza aata . barot jahan bhi jayega dost banayega kyunki vo baatein hi itni pyari karta hai . job ki party deni hai tujhe .
keep shining always
author: Bhavay  Bukkal

text:
RUSHABH GANDHI - definition of AWESOME.
Teri college life kaafi happening rahi hai , aur ho bhi kyun na tu hai hi itna accha . first year mein pair tudwane ke baad bhi practise pe aaya tha tu . teri decision making itni acchi kaise hai bhai . mujhe first year mein hi pata lag gaya tha ki tujh mein coordi wali qualities hain ( CAPTAIN). jitni acchi yaadein banayi hain utne khatarnak kaand bhi kiye hain tune ( women cell) . anatargni mein jab panic attacks hote the mujhe to seedha tere aur rawat ke paas aata tha , shayad isliye bond itna strong hai humara kyunki kharab time mein bohot support kiya hai tune . 
I am so glad that our paths crossed in this life . kuch rishte apne khoon se bhi upar hote hain vaisa hai apna rishta . 
I am pretty sure GANDHI KI AANDHI mein poori mumbai udd jayegi .
#GANDHIGAWD
author: Bhavay  Bukkal

text:
bhai tere jaisa  pyara aur bhola aadmi kaise ban gaya president . chaapne ki saari seemayein paar kar di hain tumne .H.R KADIM ko bhi surpass kar diya bhai tune . antaragni kar li , acads mein phod diya , president ban gaya and what not. par in sabse zyada important baat ye hai ki tu humble hi raha throughout .you are a good person with a beautiful soul.
 I know in coming years you will be so big that i wil be telling some dude "NIKUNJ KOTHARI WAS MY BATCHMATE". 
ps: interIIT mein battle ke time ka interview yaad hai XD.

text:
pandey jitna koi chaap dega to vo insaan god level surpass kar dega .tera electrical wala paper same to same chaap diya tha maine com mein . jaipur mein yaad hai autowala takkar maar gaya tha tujhe . itna legendaary aadmi hai tu fir bhi itna humble .BBOY bhi ban gaya tha second year mein . hum log kitni bhi mehnat kar lein pandey se 100 kadam peeche rahenge .pandey ke paas itna paisa hai ki aadha U.P khareed le .pandey jo kaam thaan leta hai vo poora karke hi maanta hai. accha aadmi hai pandey tu , kabhi luchnow aaunga to tere ghar zaroor aaunga milne . 
zindagi mein kabhi bhi kuch dikkat ya pareshani ho to group pe baat kar lena , problem ka solution nahi bhi milega to bhi kam se kam B.T share kar lenge .
hum dono humesha corresponding lagte the isliye apna alag connection hai .
aage bhi tu aise hi chaapta rahega ye hum sabko pata hai bas bhool mat jana doston ko.

keep shining SASHA <3 .

author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Gandhi bhai...
Degree dilwane ke lie dhanyawaad...yaad bhi nahi ki kitne topics pdhaye hai tune, kitne exams mai cheating krayi and kitne courses pass krwaye
Uske alawa bhi hmesha saath dia bhai...IME project mai sath mai kuch nahi kia tha, TA project mai sath mai gand mrayi thi, library mi sath finance pdha tha, barclays mai sath mai ktaya tha, bc resume ke projects bhi sare same the or fr dono jakr OYO mai hi phasee
BC kitni chize hai sari likh bhi nahi paunga.....civil ki labs mai kitni maa chudai hai, environmental mai pura time bkchodi kaati thi ,  intern pr OYO ko gaali dete the, flipkart ki deck discuss krte the
Placement season mai mere randi rone sunne ke lie koi nahi tha pr tjhpr trust tha bhai....jb bhi frust hota tha to tjhe text kr leta tha and sari companies ko gaali deta tha tere samne
Bad mai bhi 7th 8th semester mai sare courses tere hi bhrose the...pata tha ki kuch bhi hoga to tu jo bolega wo mark krna hai 
Ye likh deta hu taki tjhe yad rhe ki tune uss din mjhe apna peg pilaya tha kyuki tu to bhand tha, pata nahi abhi yaad bhi hoga xD
Ye memoir ki wse hume jrurt pdni nahi chahiye kyuki abhi bhot lmba jana hai...
Goa ki trip baki hai and
Mumbai mai kitab likhne jitne kaand krne hai <3
Tab tk chill marta reh and logo ki help krta reh!!
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Sir Pranaam!!
Ajay ya shashwat ki wajah se hi mile the prr dheere dheere kafi batein hone lagi thi. Bhot positive banda hai yar tu, isliye hmesha sahi rha tere sath hangout krna, teri intern ke bare mai shyd hmari bat na hui ho pr mne tera example bhot logo ko chipkaya hai and khud bhi inspire hua tha usse....
Uske bad to hmesha bhaiya ke jokes pr hasna yad hai aur google meet pr cheating krna.
Axis ka result aate hi mne sbse phle tjhe hi call kia tha pr tune phle hi guess krlia isliye mai mze nahi le paya.
SSAC lgne ki bat pr sbse phle tjhe hi phone kia tha, ye sochkr ki tu bacha lega pr acha hua uski jrurt nhi padi
Last din bhi sahi tha yar, or aage aane wale dino ke lie sahi foundation set krdi thi.....Jaldi hi milte hai mumbai mai
Api positivity and creativity bacha kr rkhna...cheers bhai

AniSoc, now a club is something I kept wishing to be a part of since I came to IITK, albeit you were the closest I got to it. Anime brought us both to FLP, and that's what started our friendship. I'm glad I had your awesome company during FLP, along with Avinash and Rashmi senpai. 

Our stop-motion collab never came to life, though it was fantastic in my imaginations. Maybe one day while scrolling FB or insta we might see something. Cheers to that hope :)
author: Chirag  Kapoor

text:
Hello! We, the dual degree peeps, are being forced to write memoirs to each other when these could be so much more senti when we really were leaving the campus. It's tough to put my mind to think this is going to our last meet, and so let me write to our three years of friendship. 

Since you didn't remember how our friendship started, I'll let you know. It began with the Macro-I graph assignment. Vaibhav told you I am a nerd for excel/sheets graph, and you came to me for help. Then I came to you for notes and stuff, and that started our journey. 

I have always seen you as an ambitious girl who has successfully cleared what life had to throw at her. You are different from most people and in a good way. We don't have many memories yet except for studying together to start taking the same courses and finally having the same thesis. Our path keeps converging. 

Let's see where the future takes us. Destiny is all xD.

Bob opened up his chips in class, releasing cheesy air - His teacher asked, "Is there enough so everyone can share?"

He didn't have enough within the bag that he had brought - He sighed as he replied, "I'll look to see just what I've got."
